  <brief_title>Glenohumeral Cortisone Injection</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized Controlled Pilot Study Evaluating the Efficacy of Early Glenohumeral Cortisone Injection in Patients With Shoulder Stiffness Following Proximal Humerus Fractures</official_title>
