  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The objective of this project is to determine if giving a cortisone injection to patients
      with proximal humerus fractures who have stiff shoulders recover their range of motion.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      THis is a randomized control trial to determine if giving a cortisone injection to patients
      with proximal humerus fractures who have stiff shoulders recover their range of motion.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
